Class MediumName

  • Object
    • CodeList<MediumName>
      • MediumName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MediumName>, ControlledVocabulary
    @Deprecated
@UML(identifier="MD_MediumNameCode",
     specification=ISO_19115,
     version=2003)
public final class MediumName
extends CodeList<MediumName>
    Deprecated.
    This code list is not anymore part of ISO 19115:2014, since MediumName has been replaced by Citation. This change may be applied in GeoAPI 4.0. See issue #14.
    Name of the medium.
    Since:
    2.0

      • valueOf

        public static MediumName valueOf​(String code)
        Deprecated.
        Returns the medium name that matches the given string, or returns a new one if none match it. More specifically, this methods returns the first instance for which name().equals(code) returns true. If no existing instance is found, then a new one is created for the given name.
        Parameters:
        code - the name of the code to fetch or to create.
        Returns:
        a code matching the given name.
